thread.title: Soap Emmerdale

author: Fiona Flynn
title: Soap Emmerdale
text: Aaron is not a happy bunny as you can see in the picture following on from his arrest last night, and while the Dingles rally around Chas, Diane says she'll never be able to forgive her for not telling the truth. Chas has a few other problems to deal with tonight though when she wakes in the early hours to discover that someone has broken in and starts to worry that whoever shot Robert is targeting her. Or... does she have a jealous ex on her hands? I mean not pointing any fingers, but that Emma definitely has it in her.
